name: Vintage leather doctors bag Gladstone bag morbid curio mortician
description:
Vintage leather doctors bag / Gladstone bag. Found at a flea market in the heart of Paris. 
Original lining with reconditioned handle.  Estimated to be from the late twenties early thirties. These bags are amazing for fitting a lot into with large comfy handles that take the brunt of the weight.  They are the original Mary Poppins bag in the way that you can fit a fair few outfits, books, beach things and maybe hatstand (not really a hat stand, don't try that!) 
Closes so safe and securely with a push clasp and two clip over locks at each end of the handle.  
To care for your vintage bag, you can use a light leather oil or saddle soap.  The skull in the picture is slightly smaller than life sized so that gives you an idea of size.  The leather is a rich brown colour and the inside lining is pale green.  As this is a vintage item and has many years of history, it does have a few knocks and the lining is slightly stained.  However this adds to the overall look of the piece.

name: Clear quartz and purple amethyst full moon charged crystal necklace
description:
Clear quartz and purple amethyst full moon charged crystal necklace.

Crystals are known for their healing and deflective energy powers.
These crystals are all full moon charged so will be full of power and energy. 

Purple Amethyst has been highly esteemed throughout the ages for its stunning beauty and legendary powers to stimulate and soothe the mind and emotions. It is a semi-precious stone in today’s classifications but to the ancients it was a “Gem of Fire,” a Precious Stone worth, at times in history, as much as a Diamond. It has always been associated with February, the month the Romans dedicated to Neptune, their water-god, and is the traditional birthstone of that month. It is the stone of St. Valentine and faithful love, and signifies ecclesiastical dignity as the Bishop’s Stone. It carries the energy of fire and passion, creativity and spirituality, yet bears the logic of temperance and sobriety. [Fernie, 170-171][Mella, 73][Eason, 212]


Clear Quartz is known as the "master healer" and will amplify energy and thought, as well as the effect of other crystals.  It absorbs, stores, releases and regulates energy.  Clear Quartz draws off negative energy of all kinds, neutralising background radiation, including electromagnetic smog or petrochemical emanations.  It balances and revitalises the physical, mental, emotional and spiritual planes.  Cleanses and enhances the organs and subtle bodies and acts as a deep soul cleanser, connecting the physical dimension with the mind.  Clear Quartz enhances psychic abilities.  It aids concentration and unlocks memory.  Stimulates the immune system and brings the body into balance.  Clear Quartz (Crystal Quartz, Rock Crystal) harmonises all the chakras and aligns the subtle bodies.

Crystals are mounted on 30inch long Stirling silver chains which close with a lobster clasp. All crystals are different so no two will ever be the same.  They range between 1inch to 3inches in length. 

Chains can be made shorter on request.
